        </div>
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2><code>GetMessageSignature</code></h2>
            <br />
            <h4>Description</h4>
            <p>
                This endpoint generates a signature for a given message using a private key provided by the FalconWrapper library.
            </p>
            <br />
            <h4>Endpoint</h4>

            <h4><strong><code>GET /api/GetMessageSignature?message={message}&private_key_str={private_key_str}</code></strong></h4>
            <br />
            <h4>Parameters</h4>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-bordered table-hover">
                    <thead>
                        <tr style="text-align:center; background-color: gray">
                            <th style="color: #fff">Parameter</th>
                            <th style="color: #fff">Type</th>
                            <th style="color: #fff">Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr style="text-align: center;">
                            <td>message</td>
                            <td>string</td>
                            <td>The string/text message to be signed.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="text-align:center;">
                            <td>private_key_str</td>
                            <td>string</td>
                            <td>The private key for signing.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <br />
            <h4>Responses</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <b>200 OK:</b>
                    Returns the generated signature.
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Content-Type: application/json
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Body: Signature object <br />
                            <code>
                                {<br />
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"logn": 10,<br />
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"message": "YourMessage",<br />
                                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"signature_str": "GeneratedSignature"<br />
                                }<br />
                            </code>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <b>400 Bad Request:</b>
                    If either <b>'message'</b> or <b>'private_key_str'</b> parameters are missing.
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Content-Type: application/problem+json
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Body: Error message
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <b>500 Internal Server Error:</b>
                    If an error occurs during signature generation.
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            Content-Type: application/problem+json
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            Body: Error message
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
            <br />
            <h4>Example</h4><br />
            <h5>Request</h5>
            <h5><strong><code style="color:green">GET /api/GetMessageSignature?message=Hello&private_key_str=E7C12F...</code></strong></h5>
            <h5>Response</h5>
            <code>
                {<br />
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"logn": 10,<br />
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"message": "Hello",<br />
                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"signature_str": "ABCD1234..."<br />
                }<br />
            </code>
            <br />
            <h4>Models</h4>
            <h5>Signature</h5>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-bordered table-hover">
                    <thead>
                        <tr style="text-align:center; background-color: gray">
                            <th style="color: #fff">Field</th>
                            <th style="color: #fff">Type</th>
                            <th style="color: #fff">Description</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr style="text-align: center;">
                            <td>logn</td>
                            <td>int</td>
                            <td>Logarithm value used for signature generation.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="text-align:center;">
                            <td>message</td>
                            <td>string</td>
                            <td>The message/string that was signed.</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="text-align:center;">
                            <td>signature_str</td>
                            <td>string</td>
                            <td>The generated signature.</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <br />
            <h4>Notes</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>The signature is generated using the FalconWrapper library with a logarithm value of 10.</li>
                <li>If either <b>'message'</b> or <b>'private_key_str'</b> parameters are missing, a bad request error will be returned.</li>
                <li>If an error occurs during signature generation, an error message will be returned instead of the signature.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

